commit.message:
add db backend & abstract imageops

- abstract imgurAddImage and isImageUrl into imageOps.addUrl
- fix isImageUrl to handle more cases
- add mongoOps.js to handle db operations on mongoDB databases
- update datastoreOps & server.js to communicate using more flexible API
- update dependencies & bump package-lock

change command format

use semicolon to avoid collision with discord emoji
list macros, update help, fix embed text
